      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "for i=0:\n    s[0] = \"p\" -> use the ASCII Value = 112\n    t[0] = \"t\" -> use the ASCII Value = 116\n\n    if(m1[112] != m2[116]){break}\n    \n    m1[112] = 0+1\n    m2[116] = 0+1\n\nm1 = [0..............112..............256] = {0..............1..............256}\nm2 = [0.................116...........256] = {0................1............256}",
      "fontSize": 20,
