      "originalText": "for i=1:\n    s[1] = \"a\" -> use the ASCII Value = 97\n    t[1] = \"i\" -> use the ASCII Value = 105\n\n    if(m1[97] != m2[105]){break}\n    \n    m1[97] = 1+1 = 2\n    m2[105] = 1+1 = 2\n\nm1 = [0.........97....112..............256] = {0.........2....1..............0}\nm2 = [0.............105...116...........256] = {0.............2...1...........0}",
